<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 08:09:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列加沙战争即将结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</link><description>内阁成员表示，以色列国防军尚未实现任何一项战争目标。每个人对于第二天要做什么都有不同的想法，而其他人则担心可能会发生什么。以色列领导层缺乏凝聚力</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府在北方的承诺可能会让军事力量成为唯一选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-governments-promises-in-north-could-leave-military-force-as-the-only-option/0000018c-d60e-ddba-abad-d6af72280000</link><description>政府和军队承诺采取行动改变北部局势，可能会将以色列推向更广泛的军事对抗 ■ 随着加沙战争进入第三阶段，关于释放人质的另一项协议的谈判似乎陷入困境</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-governments-promises-in-north-could-leave-military-force-as-the-only-option/0000018c-d60e-ddba-abad-d6af72280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质于 10 月 7 日被谋杀，尸体被关押在加沙，他的基布兹称</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-establishes-team-to-investigate-hamas-october-7-attacks/0000018c-d781-daf6-a5df-d7fd37c00000</link><description>以色列人质塔米尔·阿达尔 (Tamir Adar) 的基布兹称，他于 10 月 7 日被谋杀 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部：以色列国防军在西岸开火，导致 17 岁男子死亡，四人受伤 ■ 多国警告后，胡塞武装无人机在红海爆炸 ■ 以色列国防部长：巴勒斯坦人战后加沙将由以色列人而非以色列人负责。 ■ 自10 月7 日以来，以色列境内至少有1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 22,313 人死亡、57,296 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-establishes-team-to-investigate-hamas-october-7-attacks/0000018c-d781-daf6-a5df-d7fd37c00000</guid></item><item><title>即使在哈马斯的囚禁中，她也照亮了整个房间：卡梅尔·盖特仍然在加沙被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-in-captivity-she-lights-up-the-room-carmel-gat-is-still-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018c-d6a1-ddba-abad-d6a1ba470000</link><description>卡梅尔·盖特以其非凡的力量和决心而闻名。与她一起被哈马斯囚禁的人质说，她通过瑜伽和冥想课程帮助他们保持理智。她的许多朋友要求不要把她抛在后面</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 23:34:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-in-captivity-she-lights-up-the-room-carmel-gat-is-still-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018c-d6a1-ddba-abad-d6a1ba470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有实施种族灭绝，但它有种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-isnt-committing-a-genocide-but-it-has-genocidaires/0000018c-d643-daf6-a5df-d77fccc00000</link><description>以色列的行动旨在摧毁哈马斯这个组织，而不是加沙的巴勒斯坦人民。真正让我担心的是以色列政界人士中担任弥赛亚派的高级职务，他们认为这场战争是犹太人民昭然命运的实现</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 22:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-isnt-committing-a-genocide-but-it-has-genocidaires/0000018c-d643-daf6-a5df-d77fccc00000</guid></item><item><title>“28 岁时，我被赶出了美国。我必须在日本和以色列之间做出选择”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-05/ty-article/.highlight/i-was-kicked-out-of-america-when-i-was-28-i-had-to-choose-between-japan-and-israel/0000018c-d646-daf6-a5df-d77e9a100000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名日本人和一名美国人来到以色列在战争中表示支持和志愿服务</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 22:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-05/ty-article/.highlight/i-was-kicked-out-of-america-when-i-was-28-i-had-to-choose-between-japan-and-israel/0000018c-d646-daf6-a5df-d77e9a100000</guid></item><item><title>炸毁数百万美元：摩萨德对哈马斯和真主党资金的秘密战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blowing-up-millions-of-dollars-the-mossads-secret-war-on-hamas-and-hezbollah-funds/0000018c-d5af-daf6-a5df-d7ff58b30000</link><description>多年来，乌迪·利维领导摩萨德的一个部门，负责监控恐怖组织的资金流向。该部队凭借创造性的方法和几乎没有任何限制，成功阻止了向哈马斯和真主党转移巨额资金。然后就被关掉了</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blowing-up-millions-of-dollars-the-mossads-secret-war-on-hamas-and-hezbollah-funds/0000018c-d5af-daf6-a5df-d7ff58b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方要求受害者和目击者就哈马斯性暴力问题作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ask-victims-and-witnesses-to-testify-about-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-d580-d751-ad8d-ffa4acf40000</link><description>10月7日哈马斯性暴力事件的大多数受害者被杀害、被扣为人质或处于心理困扰状态而无法作证。以色列警方调查人员现呼吁公众鼓励活着的受害者或目击者与他们联系并提供证据</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ask-victims-and-witnesses-to-testify-about-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-d580-d751-ad8d-ffa4acf40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事情报局局长：我们可以打击“从加沙到伊朗”的敌人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-intelligence-chief-we-can-strike-our-enemies-from-gaza-to-iran/0000018c-d5e4-daf6-a5df-d7fc29410000</link><description>哈马斯一名高级官员在贝鲁特因以色列袭击而被暗杀后，阿哈龙·哈利瓦少将在讲话中告诉情报官员课程的新毕业生“永远表达你的专业意见”。始终、无处不在、针对任何级别或梯队”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:33:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-intelligence-chief-we-can-strike-our-enemies-from-gaza-to-iran/0000018c-d5e4-daf6-a5df-d7fc29410000</guid></item><item><title>“此刻同情更重要”：以色列抗议艺术家受到人质的启发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/compassion-is-more-important-now-the-israeli-protest-artist-inspired-by-the-hostages/0000018c-d4f0-daf6-a5df-d7fcdcc00000</link><description>泽夫·恩格尔梅尔 (Zeev Engelmayer) 最出名的是他的激进主义人物肖什克 (Shoshke)，直到 10 月 7 日，肖什克都是反政府抗议活动中的熟悉人物。不过，自黑色星期六以来，他每天都画明信片，反映他对战争的希望和恐惧，特别是关于哈马斯扣押的人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/compassion-is-more-important-now-the-israeli-protest-artist-inspired-by-the-hostages/0000018c-d4f0-daf6-a5df-d7fcdcc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列选择英国法律专家在国际法院种族灭绝案中代表以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-chooses-british-legal-expert-to-represent-it-in-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-d5e5-d751-ad8d-ffe5b4880000</link><description>以色列法律专家表示，马尔科姆·肖教授必须辩称，以色列实际上遵守了国际法，以色列领导人的极端言论并不反映加沙的官方政策</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-chooses-british-legal-expert-to-represent-it-in-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-d5e5-d751-ad8d-ffe5b4880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，自 10 月 7 日以来失踪的三名以色列人被绑架到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/three-israeli-civilians-missing-since-october-7-were-kidnapped-to-gaza-idf-says/0000018c-d5ee-ddba-abad-d7effb590000</link><description>三名被绑架的以色列人被确认为 56 岁的伊兰·韦斯 (Ilan Weiss)、来自特拉维夫的 42 岁的哈南·亚布隆卡 (Hanan Yablonka) 和 28 岁的伊丹·什蒂维 (Idan Shtivi)</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:45:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/three-israeli-civilians-missing-since-october-7-were-kidnapped-to-gaza-idf-says/0000018c-d5ee-ddba-abad-d7effb590000</guid></item><item><title>你不会通过否认哈马斯强奸以色列人来解放巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-04/ty-article/.highlight/you-wont-free-palestine-by-denying-hamas-raped-israelis/0000018c-d582-ddba-abad-d7a3d6510000</link><description>你可以拆开每个证人的证词，手摇每一个被剥光尸体的视频，并告诉每个愿意听的人，哈马斯不会这样做。但这不会抹去受害者在最后一刻所承受的痛苦，也不会解放巴勒斯坦</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-04/ty-article/.highlight/you-wont-free-palestine-by-denying-hamas-raped-israelis/0000018c-d582-ddba-abad-d7a3d6510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸难民营，审问数百名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-west-bank-refugee-camp-interrogates-hundreds-of-palestinians/0000018c-d583-ddba-abad-d7a3b2a70000</link><description>这是以色列国防军在努尔沙姆斯难民营开展的最长的行动，自战争开始以来，该难民营的军事活动不断增加。据报道，两名以色列士兵和几名巴勒斯坦人在行动中受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:32:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-west-bank-refugee-camp-interrogates-hundreds-of-palestinians/0000018c-d583-ddba-abad-d7a3b2a70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：巴勒斯坦人将对战后加沙负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-palestinian-players-to-be-responsible-for-gaza-after-war/0000018c-d59a-ddba-abad-d7bbc7660000</link><description>以色列国防部长约阿夫·加兰特在以色列战时内阁就巴勒斯坦飞地计划进行首次讨论之前表示，“战争目标实现后，以色列将不会在加沙地带出现任何民事存在”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-palestinian-players-to-be-responsible-for-gaza-after-war/0000018c-d59a-ddba-abad-d7bbc7660000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列对加沙的破坏中，出现了一种新的反人类罪：杀戮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/amid-israeli-destruction-in-gaza-a-new-crime-against-humanity-emerges-domicide/0000018c-d585-d751-ad8d-ffa5965e0000</link><description>以色列在加沙的猛烈轰炸行动的观察者们引用了“杀戮”一词。蓄意、系统地破坏房屋和基本基础设施很快就会在法律上被定义为反人类罪——以色列将何去何从？</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/amid-israeli-destruction-in-gaza-a-new-crime-against-humanity-emerges-domicide/0000018c-d585-d751-ad8d-ffa5965e0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗核武器、10 月 7 日和内塔尼亚胡：鲁莽的遗产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/irans-nukes-october-7-and-netanyahu-a-reckless-legacy/0000018c-d4a9-d4e1-ad8f-fcb9c7000000</link><description>正如以色列总理拒绝为导致哈马斯屠杀的鲁莽行为承担责任一样，他也拒绝为放弃他自己视为毕生使命的问题承担责任。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/irans-nukes-october-7-and-netanyahu-a-reckless-legacy/0000018c-d4a9-d4e1-ad8f-fcb9c7000000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院命令政府部长放弃解雇以色列邮政主席</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/supreme-court-orders-government-ministers-to-abandon-israel-post-chairman-firing/0000018c-d4e9-daf6-a5df-d7fd6be90000</link><description>两名利库德集团议员坚持在战争期间解雇以色列邮政主席米沙尔·瓦克宁，尽管有证据表明邮政服务在他的指挥下正在改善。瓦克宁和《华盛顿邮报》认为，推翻他的企图是政治性的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:18:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/supreme-court-orders-government-ministers-to-abandon-israel-post-chairman-firing/0000018c-d4e9-daf6-a5df-d7fd6be90000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院指控以色列犯有种族灭绝：请愿书、先例和惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-at-the-icj-petition-precedents-and-punishment/0000018c-d449-ddba-abad-d6e91a480000</link><description>南非为何向海牙国际法院提交针对以色列在加沙行为的请愿书？为什么以色列有兴趣配合诉讼程序？可能的结果是什么？</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-at-the-icj-petition-precedents-and-punishment/0000018c-d449-ddba-abad-d6e91a480000</guid></item><item><title>格罗斯曼、齐泽克等公众人物签署反对“巴勒斯坦人和以色列人非人化”的信</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/public-figures-sign-letter-against-the-dehumanization-of-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018c-d47c-ddba-abad-d6fdf7d20000</link><description>“亲人类阵营联盟”反对“10月7日犯下的暴行”，也反对将所有加沙人与哈马斯等同起来，“哈马斯利用哈马斯为不分青红皂白的杀戮和拒绝人道主义援助合理化”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/public-figures-sign-letter-against-the-dehumanization-of-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018c-d47c-ddba-abad-d6fdf7d20000</guid></item></channel></rss>